data.description: Welcome home to low maintenance lifestyle with peaceful pond and fountain views. End unit, so lots of windows and natural light. Jack & Jill bath on 2nd floor. Newer scratch resistant PVC flooring, & tile flooring (only carpet left is stairs, master suit and 1 upstairs bed). Exterior just painted. Gas fireplace. Main level primary bedroom & laundry. Back patio with peaceful wooded view.  Great layout, great storage, very well kept. Quiet neighborhood. Great location to Monon, Fort Ben Park, Downtown, Broad Ripple, Castleton, Glendale & Keystone shopping & restaurants. Easy access to 465. Don't miss out on this great opportunity where the exterior & landscaping are taken care of!
